            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">These are the seven points we emphasize with teams in Google. We hope they are useful to you as you think through your own ML-powered product questions. As ML starts to power more and more products and experiences, let’s step up to our responsibility to stay human-centered, find the unique value for people, and make every experience great.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
